<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rḥmẗ ktẖyraⁿạ ạrḥmny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rḥmẗ ktẖyraⁿạ ạrḥmny .. rạ̉fẗaⁿ trạ̉f ʿlỹ
 ạ̹gẖsln qlby mn ạ̹tẖmy .. qd sqṭt ạ̉ḥsn ạ̹ly
 ạlqrạr- (yạ rby ạqbl ly twbty .. ạgẖsl bdmk kẖṭyty
 brwḥk ạlqdws ạljlyl .. jdd ly ʿhd mḥbty)2
 2- f ậtẖạmy dwmạ ạ̉mạmy .. tsḥq ʿẓmy yạ yswʿ
 qd zạdt fy thy ẓlạmy .. hlạ tạ̉ty drb ạlrjwʿ
 3- rd ly bhjẗ kẖlạṣk .. qd fqdthạ sydy
 tqbãl dẖbyḥẗ nfsy .. mḥrqạtiⁿ lạ trtḍy</lyrics>
<author>tsẖạrly qsṭẗ, sylạ ḥdạd</author>
<hymn_number>8510</hymn_number>
</song>